text: Nathalie Desmares (born 18 May 1972) is a French snowboarder. She was born in L'Aigle. She competed at the 1998 Winter Olympics in Nagano, in women's giant slalom, and she competed at the 2010 Winter Olympics in Vancouver, in women's parallel giant slalom. Desmares competed in the Parallel giant slalom with Sylvain Dufour as a partner in 2018. == References == == External links == * Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:People from Normandy Category:French female snowboarders Category:Olympic snowboarders of France Category:Snowboarders at the 1998 Winter Olympics Category:Snowboarders at the 2010 Winter Olympics
